title: (Thurs Early Bird) Lunchbox Try's Amy's Daughter Donut Hack + We Play Elder vs. Millennial + Mailbag: Pregnancy Announcement Same Day As Sisters Birthday Party
itunes:title: (Thurs Early Bird) Lunchbox Try's Amy's Daughter Donut Hack + We Play Elder vs. Millennial + Mailbag: Pregnancy Announcement Same Day As Sisters Birthday Party
description:
A few days ago, Amy told us how her daughter discovered a hack at Dunkin Donuts to make some extra money, Lunchbox tests it out for himself to see if it really works. Plus, We play Elder vs. Millennial and the loser has to eat a disgusting gummy. Bobby opens the mailbag and helps a listener who planned to announce her pregnancy on the same day as her sister's birthday since all their family will be together, but she isn't sure if her sister will be happy sharing the attention with her.  

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
